      "description": "This car is in poor condition. The exterior has multiple visible dents, scratches, and signs of significant wear. The interior is heavily worn, with damaged seating surfaces and deteriorated trim. Mechanical systems have notable issues that will require attention, and the car should be inspected thoroughly before purchase.",
